OL,3,CWelsh researchers develop new test for
OL,4,Cthe most common cancer amongst men
OL,6,FA first-of-its-kind lateral flow test
OL,7,Fto detect prostate cancer within
OL,8,Fminutes is being developed by
OL,9,Fresearchers in Wales.
OL,11,FIt's hoped the test - which could be
OL,12,Ftaken at a GP surgery or at home - can
OL,13,Fbe rolled out into a nationwide
OL,14,Fscreening programme that could help
OL,15,Fsave thousands of lives and the NHS
OL,16,Fmillions of pounds every year.
