OL,3,CWelsh researchers develop new test for
OL,4,Cthe most common cancer amongst men
OL,6,FScientists at Aberystwyth University
OL,7,Ffound that several key changes, or
OL,8,Fbiomarkers, in the urine of men with
OL,9,Fprostate cancer offer a far superior
OL,10,Fdiagnostic accuracy compared to the
OL,11,Fblood-based PSA laboratory test
OL,12,Fcurrently used by the NHS.
OL,14,FValley Diagnostics, based in Cardiff,
OL,15,Fhas the exclusive rights to
OL,16,Fcommercialise the biomarker research,
OL,17,Fand is working with the university to
OL,18,Ftranslate their findings into the
OL,19,Flateral flow test.
