OL,3,CWelsh researchers develop new test for
OL,4,Cthe most common cancer amongst men
OL,6,FDave Taylor, CEO of Valley
OL,7,FDiagnostics, said: "This has the
OL,8,Fpotential to completely transform the
OL,9,Fway we test for prostate cancer,
OL,10,Fsaving thousands of lives and easing
OL,11,Fthe pressure on the NHS.
OL,13,F"It is cost-effective and reliable,
OL,14,Fproviding immediate results that allow
OL,15,Ffor effective patient triage without
OL,16,Fthe need for additional lab testing.
OL,18,F"This could reduce patient stress and
OL,19,Finconvenience, cut manpower and costs
OL,20,Fand eliminate unnecessary waiting
OL,21,Ftimes and clinical visits."
