OL,3,CWelsh researchers develop new test for
OL,4,Cthe most common cancer amongst men
OL,6,FProfessor Luis Mur, who heads the
OL,7,FOSCAR study at Aberystwyth University,
OL,8,Fsaid: "The ever-increasing awareness
OL,9,Fof the risks of prostate cancer for
OL,10,Fmen has highlighted the need for a
OL,11,Fnational screening programme.
OL,12,FUnfortunately, the tests currently
OL,13,Favailable are not suitable for such a
OL,14,Fprogramme.
