OL,3,CWelsh researchers develop new test for
OL,4,Cthe most common cancer amongst men
OL,6,F"The biomarkers we have found will
OL,7,Fallow us to develop a groundbreaking
OL,8,Ftest that could be used in a GP
OL,9,Fsurgery or even at home. We expect
OL,10,Fthis will lead to a paradigm shift in
OL,11,Fprostate cancer detection which could
OL,12,Fsave lives. The increased accuracy of
OL,13,Fthis test could prevent men undergoing
OL,14,Funnecessary treatments and save the
OL,15,FNHS money."
OL,17,FValley Diagnostics is currently
OL,18,Fseeking equity and grant funding to
OL,19,Fcontinue the development of a
OL,20,Fprototype of the lateral flow test.
